Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.90,0:00:14.93,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.15,0:00:15.24,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.91,0:00:18.79,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.45,0:00:23.12,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.12,0:00:26.75,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.75,0:00:30.51,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.51,0:00:33.68,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.05,0:00:36.80,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.80,0:00:40.27,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.35,0:00:44.94,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.94,0:00:48.44,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.44,0:00:51.07,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.15,0:00:54.65,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.82,0:00:59.45,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.45,0:01:02.79,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.29,0:01:11.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:13.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil\NShocker, a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.24,0:01:15.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,organization plotting\Nworld domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.13,0:01:18.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.83,0:01:24.72,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\an7\c&H000000&\3c&H334561&}Tokyo Penitentiary
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.80,0:01:31.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This prison houses a man\Nserving a life sentence
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.23,0:01:34.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,for atrocious crimes such\Nas armed robbery and murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.06,0:01:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wake up. It's 6 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.17,0:01:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, No. 13.\NThat's your wake-up call!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.71,0:01:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.64,0:02:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.08,0:02:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to wake up\Nat 6 o'clock every day?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.71,0:02:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You piece of trash...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.00,0:02:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.13,0:02:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been here for five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.44,0:02:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How long are you\Ngoing to keep me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.50,0:02:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.72,0:02:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're serving a life\Nsentence, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.77,0:02:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.70,0:02:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.58,0:02:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't keep me here anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.85,0:02:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.41,0:02:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Open up! Open up, damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.40,0:02:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Open this door!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.63,0:02:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you hear me, you bastard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.33,0:02:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.58,0:02:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.16,0:02:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.90,0:02:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.23,0:02:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker has long sought a man\Nof your cold-hearted brutality.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.83,0:02:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,To plunge the world into chaos\Nand bring humanity to heel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.25,0:02:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds fun to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.87,0:03:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll join you,\Nif you'll have me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.69,0:03:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be made to bathe in poisonous\Nmushroom extract for one week's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.91,0:03:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, take him away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.68,0:03:38.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And so, one week passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.05,0:03:50.03,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs165\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(467.167,210.389)}Poisonous Monster
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.05,0:03:50.03,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs165\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(497.167,710.389)}Kinokomorg Attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.24,0:03:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Your name will henceforth\Nbe Kinokomorg.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.59,0:04:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this powder?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.16,0:04:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They're poisonous\Nmushroom spores.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.12,0:04:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Spores?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And anyone who touches\Nthose spores...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.62,0:04:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Kimiko! Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.54,0:04:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiroshi, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.03,0:04:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're both doing great!\NKeep it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.39,0:04:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.30,0:05:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.31,0:05:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Where could it have gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.67,0:05:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.17,0:05:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiroshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.23,0:05:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone, help!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Take her away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.06,0:05:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Give Kimiko back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.94,0:06:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Where could Kimiko\Nand Hiroshi have gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.25,0:06:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That mushroom monster...\NIt must be a member of Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.39,0:06:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's follow them back,\Nthen let Hayato know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.17,0:06:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! They're heading\Nfor those power lines!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.42,0:06:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's a dead end!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.65,0:06:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.97,0:06:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Where could it have gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.26,0:06:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What a mystery...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.58,0:06:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go look!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.46,0:07:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The tire tracks end here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.81,0:07:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.54,0:07:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be an\Nentrance somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.84,0:07:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't see anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.43,0:07:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.86,0:07:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never see through\Nmy special optical barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.15,0:07:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.10,0:07:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Children, kidnapped?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.33,0:07:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did the truck go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It passed under the power\Nlines, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.23,0:07:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It vanished into thin air.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.58,0:07:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.53,0:07:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Contact with\NKinokomorg's spores
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.17,0:07:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,immediately paralyzes\Nthe unfortunate victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.96,0:07:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If we bring those humans\Nback and modify them,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.17,0:07:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the world will soon\Nbelong to Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.32,0:08:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It is Shocker that gave you\Nnew life as a mushroom man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.16,0:08:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I am grateful for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.05,0:08:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Use your great power to\Nbring us more allies!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.96,0:08:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's easily done.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.78,0:08:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it all to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.28,0:08:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I love to cause\Nsuffering to humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.49,0:08:21.50,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H47652B&}Suzumi {\c&H2F378A&}Ghost Parade
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.51,0:08:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Come and see, come and see!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.07,0:08:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be scary! Very scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.54,0:08:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, come!\NCome see the scary ghost parade!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.59,0:08:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey,\Nwhat are you guys advertising?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.60,0:08:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A ghost parade!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.94,0:08:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.22,0:08:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Come join us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.31,0:08:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where are you doing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.92,0:09:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.32,0:09:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.19,0:09:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.47,0:09:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going pretty far out...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.11,0:09:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there really an\Namusement park around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.49,0:09:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.17,0:09:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.37,0:09:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a real ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.12,0:09:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.56,0:09:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Help, someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.10,0:09:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow! Hey! Someone help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.82,0:09:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.75,0:09:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Monster! Stop it! Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.35,0:09:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.13,0:09:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, take the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.55,0:10:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.38,0:12:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you done\Nwith the children?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.27,0:12:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That truck there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.18,0:12:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to save the children!\NHurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.24,0:13:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.65,0:13:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, save the children... Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not over yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.86,0:14:09.74,Bumper Episode 14-51,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs85\pos(331,454)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.66,0:14:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.49,0:14:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?\NDid you learn anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.31,0:14:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Not much, yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.67,0:14:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems to be a plant-based\Ntoxin, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.96,0:14:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a virus, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.80,0:14:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.46,0:14:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can tell it's quite toxic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.75,0:14:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Koike.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.87,0:14:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're saying that even if they\Nsurvive, they'll never recover?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.11,0:14:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me some time\Nto run more tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.94,0:14:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But what will happen to the\Nchildren in the meantime?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.19,0:15:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The spores that attach to the people\Nare not yet sufficiently contagious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.07,0:15:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Until our experiment succeeds,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.41,0:15:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,we cannot have people learning\Nthe secret of their paralysis.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.90,0:15:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You must retrieve\Nthose children at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.06,0:15:29.05,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Hiroshi and Kimiko disappeared\Nfrom the tennis court.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.66,0:15:33.58,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,And these children have been\Nunconscious all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.49,0:15:40.51,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Just what is Shocker\Nplotting to use
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.84,0:15:44.01,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,these innocent children for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.33,0:16:13.15,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Shocker! What are you\Nusing the children for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.15,0:16:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.47,0:16:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't over!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.24,0:16:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.33,0:16:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.05,0:16:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What does Shocker want with\Nthese paralyzed children?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.09,0:17:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,These children might just hold
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.08,0:17:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,the key to solving all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.22,0:17:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got it, Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.28,0:17:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.48,0:17:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.36,0:17:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The children's bodies are\Ncovered with a kind of poisonous
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.38,0:17:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,mushroom spore I've\Nnever seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.98,0:17:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Poisonous mushroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.57,0:17:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.05,0:17:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If those spores get any stronger,\Nthey might be able to reproduce.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.68,0:17:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That would have dire\Nconsequences for all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.29,0:17:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to find a medicine to fight\Nit, and soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.90,0:17:40.53,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile,\NShocker was infecting the children
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.53,0:17:42.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,with a new poisonous\Nmushroom extract.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.18,0:17:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,These children's condition\Nwill relapse in 24 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.90,0:17:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone who touches these children\Nwill be infested with the spores,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.59,0:17:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and collapse one hour later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.17,0:18:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This will lead to mass panic!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.21,0:18:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't there when I\Nwatered it this morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.46,0:18:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.00,0:18:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What if it turns\Nout to be poisonous?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.55,0:18:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.31,0:18:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a strange\Nmushroom growing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.31,0:18:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Mushroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.13,0:18:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's mechanical.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.45,0:18:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker's been listening\Nto all our conversations.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.02,0:18:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive, Ichimonji Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.62,0:18:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You caught on very quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.97,0:18:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm willing to return the\Nchildren you're looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.54,0:18:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.23,0:18:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying I'll\Nreturn the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.88,0:18:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Come and get them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.00,0:18:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Name the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.93,0:18:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.65,0:18:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This could be a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.93,0:18:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you afraid,\NIchimonji Hayato?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.90,0:18:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Name the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.14,0:19:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.00,0:19:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He's taken the bait, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.57,0:19:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.93,0:19:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want us to spare the children,\Nyou'll need to join Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.52,0:19:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You really think\NI'll agree to that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.38,0:19:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you rather watch\Nthe children die?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.81,0:19:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.68,0:19:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You fiends!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.52,0:19:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.08,0:20:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.44,0:20:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.45,0:21:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.86,0:21:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider! Where are the children?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.36,0:21:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.56,0:21:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.05,0:21:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.20,0:21:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.11,0:21:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.33,0:21:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.21,0:22:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!\NWe got the children out safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.61,0:22:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of here, fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.68,0:22:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.89,0:22:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.45,0:22:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.06,0:23:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll put an end to the\NKamen Rider at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.55,0:23:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.33,0:23:27.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider is in his\Nmost dire straits yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.38,0:23:29.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Will Shocker finish him off?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.88,0:23:33.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,You need to get up,\Nto keep peace in our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.74,0:23:40.33,Cont,,0,0,0,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.98,0:23:42.88,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,496.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.98,0:23:44.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.52,0:23:47.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is once again the poisonous\Nmonster Kinokomorg.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.50,0:23:51.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kinokomorg has used his poison to\Nmake Ichimonji Hayato his prisoner.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.82,0:23:53.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Can our Kamen Rider\Nturn things around?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.89,0:23:56.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A stunning battle unfolds\Nin the creepy Shocker base.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.15,0:24:00.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week for\N"Defeat Kinokomorg!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.68,0:24:00.93,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs165\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(487.167,300.389)}Defeat Kinokomorg!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.87,0:24:09.71,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.30,0:24:12.30,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.30,0:24:14.26,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.26,0:24:17.31,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the\Nvillains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.81,0:24:19.68,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.68,0:24:21.56,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.56,0:24:23.35,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.35,0:24:24.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.15,0:24:27.19,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.23,0:24:32.90,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with\Nall of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.90,0:24:36.49,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.49,0:24:40.08,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.58,0:24:44.33,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:03:46.06,0:03:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Poisonous Monster\NKinokomorg Attacks!